Ing '''Thodupuzha''' (King Malayalam: തൊടുപുഴ) metung yang balen ampong [[w:Municipality|municipality]] king [[Estadu ampong teritoriu ning India|estadu]] ning [[Kerala]], [[India]]. Iti ing pekamaragul a balen ampong sentru ning kalakal king distritu. Maki dayu yang 59 km manibat king [[Ernakulam]]. Thodupuzha murin ing lagiu ning [[w:Thodupuzha river|ilug]] a mamagus king balen ning '''Thodupuzha'''.  

